  "texts": [
    "The convergence of AI 1.0 through 4.0 suggests discipline on the cusp of a profound metamorphosis, one where machines not only perceive and act in the world but might also reflect on their own goals and limitations.",
    "Whether or not full-fledged \"conscious AI\" emerges, the field's trajectory will undoubtedly redefine how we understand intelligence, innovation, and human-machine coexistence in the years to come.",
    "Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence 08 frontiersin.org"
